      "content": "i know, i know... the \"you matter\" thing. people always say that. but it doesn't change the math. if i just stopped being here tomorrow, the cafe would still be full, the city would keep moving, and nobody would even realize a seat was empty. it feels more like an illusion than actually mattering. it’s like i'm just a glitch in the system that's waiting to be corrected.",
